    "## 9 · Conclusions\n",
    "\n",
    "We have demonstrated that standard KNN suffers a **structural, dimension-independent\n",
    "bias** under class imbalance, and derived a principled correction from order statistics.\n",
    "\n",
    "The core result — $k_{eff} = r = N_{maj}/N_{min}$ — is mathematically exact under the\n",
    "Poisson-uniform assumption and dimension-free by construction. Extending it with a CV-tuned\n",
    "exponent ($\\alpha$) and joint optimisation of $(n_{votes}, \\alpha)$ produces\n",
    "**KNNFairRankJointCV**, which outperforms SMOTE+KNN statistically in G-Mean across 49\n",
    "benchmark datasets without generating any synthetic data.\n",
